hairmanship seats in three council areas already declared by the Independent National Electoral Commission (INEC). March 10, 2019 In "Elections 2019 Updates" katsina—All Progressives Congress, APC, APC, has won the Katsina North Senatorial district seat and President Muhammadu Buhari’s zone with a landslide victory, defeating the Peoples Democratic Party, PDP with over 160,000 votes. August 13, 2018 In "News"